ingredientsDesc:
OUED: 
The N Antiserum to human Apolipoprotein A-I is produced  by immunization of rabbits with highly purified human apolipoprotein A-I. The N Antiserum to Human Apolipoprotein B is produced by immunization of rabbits with LDL (density fraction 1.025 to 1.050 g/mL) obtained from human sera.
OUPG: N Apolipoprotein Standard Serum is a lyophilized reagent prepared from human serum. 
The concentrations are lot-dependent.
